<h1><!--#echo var="pagetitle"--></h1>
<p>This site contains information about how to use software
configuration management, especially version control, effectively.
</p>
<h2>Recent Changes</h2>
<ul>
<li><img src="/NEW.gif" alt="NEW!"/>Added a publications section, which includes a <a
href="pubs/hass_sidebar.html">sidebar</a> that we wrote for the new
book <a
href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0321117662/steveberczuk">
Configuration Management Principles and Practice</a>.

</li>
</ul>

